                    <msContents class="lemmatic">
                        <summary>
                            This is a lemmatically arranged commentary. The introduction begins on f. 1b; the beginning of each Book is as follows:
                            Bk1: 1b; Bk 2: 6a (ending at ii. 40; in f. 10b, Bk 2 ends at ii. 40, and then ii. 23 starts); Bk 3: 10a (starting from iii. 22's comm.); Bk 4: 12b (ending at iv. 35); Bk 5: 15b; Bk 6: 21a; Bk 7: 26b.
                            This is an incomplete copy.
                        </summary>
                       
